Matt Spenceer
ARM Mali Ecosystem

- Can do compelling interfaces in HTML instead of native
- Different form factors make it difficult to build once and ship multiple
- No standard for 2D acceleration
- TyGL https://github.com/szeged/TyGL
  * xperimental 3D rendering backend for WebKit
- Skia Ganesh: used in blink engine and used by Chrome, Firefox, Opera, Android
  * uses the GLES API defined by Khronos
  * https://code.google.com/p/skia/w/list
  * enables 2D painting with GPU
- Web app over native app to take advantage of the browser engine improvements
- Painting a page takes time
- http://www.chromium.org/blink/slimming-paint
